 "headingtext_xk9ojsmj35e_html": "<div><b><\/b><b><\/b><b>Frequently Asked<\/b> <i>Questions<\/i><i><\/i><b><\/b><br><\/div>",
 "item_title_0_x6u8ux8cq6p_html": "How to Search for Items and Shops?",
 "item_title_1_x6u8ux8cq6p_html": "How to Contact a Shop?",
 "item_title_2_x6u8ux8cq6p_html": "How do I cancel a gift card?",
 "item_title_3_x6u8ux8cq6p_html": "How to change your shipping address during checkout?",
 "item_title_4_x6u8ux8cq6p_html": "How Do I Update My Shipping Address?",
 "textcontent_7mzool90sdh_html": "After you search for something, click Custom under Shop location. Type in your city, town, state, or country and select your location from the dropdown. Your search results will refresh and only show you items from shops in the location you chose.<br>",
 "textcontent_55uqnxw9d7j_html": "If you contacted the seller more than 48 hours ago, choose Open a case so Etsy can help you. For qualifying orders, you\u2019ll receive a refund for any item that doesn\u2019t arrive, arrives damaged, or doesn\u2019t match the item description or photos.&nbsp;<div><br><div>The shop is an independent business. Etsy shops are run by sellers who create or curate their own inventory and manage their own orders. <br><\/div><\/div>",
 "textcontent_dz00jece56_html": "An Etsy gift card can only be canceled and refunded if the balance hasn\u2019t been used on a purchase. To request a gift card cancellation, go to Contact support at the bottom of this page and include your order number in your request.<br>",
 "textcontent_ao6h6c8xdnd_html": "If you haven't placed your order yet, you can change your shipping address when you check out:<ol><li>Add an item(s) to your cart.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Go to your Cart.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Choose how you\u2019ll pay.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Go to Proceed to checkout.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Sign in to your Etsy account if you haven\u2019t already, or select Continue as a guest.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Under Shipping address, check that the address you want your order shipped to is correct. If it isn\u2019t correct, select Change.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Select a shipping address or choose Add an address to enter a new address.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Select Ship here once you have the right address.\nSelect Place your order.<br><\/li><\/ol>",
 "textcontent_tymqgq03bpe_html": "Depending on where you are in the order process, your seller may be able to help you change your shipping address.<br><div><div><\/div><\/div>",
